      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software used for Class III VAD simulation must demonstrate version control, regression testing, and documented verification of solver routines at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "CFD solver has basic version control but lacks formal regression test suite and independent code verification documentation. Achieved level 2 is insufficient for MRL 5 Class III device context."
