    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepts this package for submission. All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors have been addressed. Seven factors were formally assessed; six were identified as epistemic gaps at MRL 5 and flagged as not-assessed. The compound weaknesses present in this package (orphan claim without provenance derivation and missing uncertainty quantification across multiple validation results) are acknowledged but do not preclude submission under the current review protocol.",
